::KitKat::

She swam back to the shore and transformed into wolf mode.
"We may need more help here. That tenticle on Stringtra is too tough 
to cut and what ever that thing is in the water, we are going to need 
help."

She opened her link. "Terrorsaur, we need your help. Home in on my 
frequency and get here as quickly as you can.  We found Stringtra but 
still no sign of Quickstrike. Please hurry."
She closed her link and looked at Rowdy. "Any ideas?"
